(96, 'reception', 'reception desk', 'NEMESIS Classic virtual reception desk', 'the \'reception\' app manages an incoming gateway on the NEMESIS gateway server (alpha). incoming data files arrive here and are checked by the virutal receptionist, and either admitted to another area where they can be processed, or are ejected from the sy', 'the \'reception\' app manages an incoming gateway on the NEMESIS gateway server (alpha). incoming data files arrive here and are checked by the virtual receptionist, and either admitted to another area where they can be processed, or are ejected from the system.\r\n\r\nthe receptionist script checks that the filename of the incoming file matches a regular expression, that the transfer is supported by a MISR and or Data Sharing Agreement, that the file passes a virus check. If the checks are passed. It uses the phpMail app to notify stakeholders. the file is then passed to an area where it would normally be individually processed by an individual ETL or other process.', 'images/banner_colour.png', 'rgb(220, 172, 172)', 1, NULL, 2, '', 'http://', 'localhost', '', '', 'reception', 'index.php', 'legpol.php', '/klogin/account/resecureAccount.php', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', 'no-reply@localhost', ''),
